[I] Qt bindings for libpulse

[T] pulseaudio-qt is a Qt-style wrapper for libpulse. It allows querying and
[T] manipulation of various PulseAudio objects such as Sinks, Sources and
[T] Streams. It does not wrap the full feature set of libpulse.

[U] https://github.com/KDE/pulseaudio-qt

[A] The KDE-Team
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/office extra/desktop/kde
[F] CROSS OBJDIR

[L] LGPL
[V] 1.8.1
[P] X -----5---9 162.918

[D] 94a9e8b644612591000cbb20e490b40e5b002610b99c955a2b152ef3 pulseaudio-qt-1.8.1.tar.xz https://download.kde.org/stable/pulseaudio-qt/

